                     />Matthews</persName>&apos; death in <date when="1764">1764</date> she married
                  again, this time to <persName>William Smith</persName>
                  <!-- could not decide an XML ID -->(<date from="1736" to="1824">1736–1824</date>)
                  of <placeName>Newcastle</placeName>. This second marriage was blessed by two
                  daughters, both of whom appear in <persName><ref target="/persons/pers2180.xml"
